companyInfo.introduction: Cng ty C phn Trang (TFC) c thnh lp thng 07/2004 vi ngun vn iu l ban u l 20 t ng, hot ng ch yu trong lnh vc ch bin cung cp thc phm ng lnh cht lng cao cho th trng th gii. Ngun thu ch yu ca cng ty n t nhm sn phm ng lnh ch bin sn t tm, chim 60% sn lng sn xut. Th trng nhp khu ln nht ca cng ty l chu u vi tng gi tr nhp khu xp x 300 t ng 1 nm. TFC hin ang vn hnh 10 dy chuyn sn xut v h thng kho c nng sut khong 12 tn thnh phm/ngy. Hin nay, Cng ty c khong 178 loisn phm khc nhau.

- Ngy 03/12/2015: Ngy giao dch u tin ca TFC trn Sn HNX vi gi ng ca cui phin l 36,100 ng/CP.

- Thng 08/2016: Tng vn iu l ln 168.3 t ng.
